Application Details
What does your application do? Please be as detailed as possible, and feel free to include links to image or video examples.
```
A Discord bot that backups a Discord Server and restore if the user need to restore it back.
This can help users have save servers and good for them to backup if they want to
PS: This bot is made in Chinese Traditional and is for Asia Users if they don't know how to read English
```

Data Collection
Tell us more about the data you store and process from Discord.

WHAT DISCORD DATA DO YOU STORE?
```
guild-icon
guild-id
guild-location
guild-name
guild-icon
guild-banner
guild-channels
guild-roles
```

DO YOU STORE MESSAGE CONTENT?
```
Yes
```

FOR WHAT PURPOSE(S) DO YOU STORE THE INFORMATION YOU COLLECT?
```
To restore servers from backups
To help users restore their servers
```

FOR HOW LONG DO YOU STORE IT?
```
About 6 months
```

WHAT IS THE PROCESS FOR USERS TO REQUEST DELETION OF THEIR DATA?
```
We will just delete it from the database and send prove to the users
```

Infrastructure
Tell us more about your application's infrastructure and your team's security practices.

HOW DO YOU HOST YOUR BOT?
```
VPS
```

WHAT LANGUAGE OR LIBRARY WAS YOUR BOT WRITTEN WITH?
```
JavaScript + node.js w/discord.js
```

HOW DO YOU KEEP YOUR BOT SECURE?
```
We keep it at a private server and the server isn't open to any other users or members
```

HOW CAN USERS CONTACT YOU WITH SECURITY CONCERNS AND OTHER QUESTIONS REGARDING YOUR BOT?
```
Users can join our support Discord Server or by emailing US.
```

ALL
